{
  "stem": "16473.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 243.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she, she, she had parsley soup and she spit the parsley into my soup, and I spit it back into her soup, and we had a wonderful game of it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's about as far back as I can recall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At first, when-- when we arrived in Hungary, I think-- and I'm not real clear about this-- but I think it was at that time that my mother-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] no, that's not right either.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They lived somewhere in some apartment that I-- I don't know about.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after that, it is that my mother worked in the boarding school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after my father's hat factory failed, that he couldn't find any jobs because things were getting difficult in Hungary, that he worked as a-- as a bellhop in a-- in a hotel and mother had to work in a boarding school.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was before I was two years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was-- [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Vily ?] was his nickname.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Vilmos, V-I-L-M-O-S, Kempfner.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He came from Pecs originally.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His mother remarried and so he left at an early age to go to Austria to join his older sister, who was married.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in Austria, he had a little women's store eventually.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was quite successful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then a kind of a chain came around and it wasn't as successful.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so by the time he left Vienna, he gave the store to his younger brother, who worked there with him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, he edited a literary magazine in Pecs where he came from in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he wrote poetry, he translated poetry, and wrote short stories in this literary magazine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He liked the theater, he liked to hang around with ladies from the theater.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And his friends were authors, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He liked to read.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
